Description: Handle of Rhodian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp.
Production date: 203 BC (see N. Badoud, Le temps de Rhodes, 2015, 142.)
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.31, 8. Name, Theuphanes?
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0741)
